# Node Agent Runtime Capabilities

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Coroot Node Agent 1.28.3] --> B[eBPF / Runtime Hooks]

    B --> C[Process Discovery]
    B --> D[Container Discovery]
    B --> E[CPU / Memory / Disk Metrics]
    B --> F[Network Throughput]
    B --> G[TCP Socket Monitoring]
    B --> H[Service Detection]
    B --> I[Service Topology Mapping]
    B --> J[Continuous Profiling]
    B --> K[Container Log Parsing]

    A --> L[Disabled via --disable-l7-tracing]

    L --> M[HTTP Payload Inspection]
    L --> N[TLS Decryption Hooks]
    L --> O[OpenSSL Uprobes]
    L --> P[Java TLS Hooks]
    L --> Q[gRPC Deep Inspection]

    B --> R[Prometheus Remote Write]
    R --> S[Coroot Backend]
```

