# Failure vs Workaround Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TD

    subgraph DefaultOperatorFlow[Default Coroot Operator Deployment]
        OP1[Coroot Operator]
        DSFAIL[Operator Managed Node-Agent]
        NEWVER[Node-Agent >= 1.31]
        EBPF1[Advanced eBPF / TLS / L7 Hooks]
        FAIL[CrashLoopBackOff / Verifier Reject]
    end

    OP1 --> DSFAIL
    DSFAIL --> NEWVER
    NEWVER --> EBPF1
    EBPF1 --> FAIL

    subgraph WorkaroundFlow[Validated Workaround]
        OP2[Coroot Operator]
        DISABLE[Disable Operator Node-Agent]
        CUSTOMDS[Custom Node-Agent DS]
        OLDVER[Node-Agent 1.28.3]
        NOL7[--disable-l7-tracing]
        STABLE[Stable Running on OCP 4.18]
    end

    OP2 --> DISABLE
    DISABLE --> CUSTOMDS
    CUSTOMDS --> OLDVER
    OLDVER --> NOL7
    NOL7 --> STABLE
```

