# Deploy Demo Applications

## Simple Traffic Demo

```bash
oc apply -f traffic-demo/00-traffic-demo.yaml
oc apply -f traffic-demo/01-traffic-generator.yaml
```

---

## Advanced Traffic Demo

```bash
oc apply -f traffic-demo/02-traffic-demo-advanced.yaml
oc apply -f traffic-demo/03-traffic-generator-advanced.yaml
```

---

## Online Boutique Demo

```bash
oc apply -f boutique/00-namespace.yaml

oc apply -n boutique -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/microservices-demo/main/release/kubernetes-manifests.yaml

bash boutique/01-anyuid-scc.sh

oc rollout restart deploy -n boutique

oc apply -f boutique/02-frontend-route.yaml
```

---

# Validation

## Check Node Agent Health

```bash
oc logs -n coroot \
  -l app.kubernetes.io/component=coroot-node-agent-custom \
  --tail=30
```

Expected:

```text
metrics remote write endpoint: http://coroot-coroot.coroot:8080/v1/metrics
sent metrics in XXms
```

